SQL_STMT_U.val: select X.defectdescription "DEFECT", X.DEFECTCATEGORY "CATEGORY", X.DEFECTSECTION "SEC", COUNT(*) "TOTAL" from FRAMEWISEDEFECT X where X.defectsection = ':1' AND TO_CHAR(X.CREATEDATE, 'DD/MM/YYYY') = ':2' AND X.MODELCODE = ':3' GROUP BY X.defectdescription, X.DEFECTCATEGORY, X.DEFECTSECTION ORDER BY TOTAL DESC
select distinct x.mtomapcode from modelwisemapping x
